										</svg>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="mt-2">
								<h4 class="card-title">Adjust Favicon Generation</h4>
								<p class="card-text">Use the settings window to choose the different types of favicon you want: add some that are no longer required for greater compatibility, set the favicon for Chrome/Android and their manifest, and much more.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
						<div class="card p-3 mb-2" id="card-three">
							<div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
								<div class="d-flex flex-row align-items-center">
									<div class="icon">
